'''Mislav Ježić''' (born 20 September 1952) is a [[Croatia]]n [[philosopher]] and [[Indologist]].<ref name="HE">{{citation |contribution-url=http://enciklopedija.hr/Natuknica.aspx?ID=29135 |contribution=Ježić, Mislav |title=[[Croatian Encyclopedia]] |year=1999–2009 |accessdate=May 29, 2014 |publisher=[[Leksikografski zavod Miroslav Krleža]] |language=Croatian}}</ref>
